ChemicalException - Exception in fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend
ChemicalException is an exception that indicates an error inherent to the chemical library.
This exception can be thrown for an internal error, but the user will mostly receive exception concerning a mishandling of the library.
ChemicalException(String) - Constructor for exception fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend.ChemicalException
Constructs a ChemicalException with a detail message.
ChemicalThread - Class in fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend
This class executes a reaction, it uses a reaction rule object and its ReactionRule.computeSelect() and ReactionRule.computeResult() functions to process to reactions.
ChemicalThread(ReactionRule, Solution, ThreadGroup) - Constructor for class fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.backend.ChemicalThread
Builds a ChemicalThread object.
